eter\nfor a range of spectral signatures of input astronomical sources relevant to\nBLASTPol, and provide a benchmark example of how our method can yield improved\naccuracy on measurements of the polarisation angle on the sky at submillimetre\nwavelengths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2012 21:43:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2013 00:51:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2013 20:07:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
