let. Combined with narrowband photometric\nmeasurements, XO-2b is the first hot Jupiter with evidence for both sodium and\npotassium present in the planet's atmosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2012 14:03:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
